project_descr: The project is $ 1 million, 18 month UNDP initiative to support the GoI to localize and implement the Paris Declaration on Aid effectiveness in Iraq.

outputs.output_descr: Institutionalise mechanisms for managing international assistance in line with the Paris Declaration on Aid Effectiveness in Iraq. The project will promote progress and for continued reform, in line with the Iraq aid harmonisation strategies

project_title: support goverment of iraq to implement paris declaration
